                <a href="+01-913-638-9056" class="text-color h5 d-block"><i class="ti-mobile"></i> 913-638-9056</a>
                <a href="mailto:Justin.L.Kennedy@outlook.com" class="text-color h5 d-block"><i class="ti-email"></i> Justin.L.Kennedy@outlook.com</a>
